{
  "texts": [
    "• The standard equations of the transformer self-attention are modified to consider the irregular time interval between visits.",
    "This information is separately calculated and then integrated into the visit information (Ren et al. 2021).",
    "• Traditional transformers are specifically used to create temporal representations employing time-aware attention weights.",
    "An interesting aspect is the use of a transformer for each data type (lab tests and vital signs).",
    "A later hierarchical feature fusion model is then used to integrate such temporal data with the prescription patient information (An et al. 2022)."
  ]
}